desc.en: Hangzhou Metropolitan Area Metro has opened a map of lines and stations. This map includes subway lines and rail transit lines in Hangzhou, Shaoxing and Haining. This map updates most of the details and proportions.

updateHistory.reason: Change line name and railway or airport style. Also fixing English names.

This map has been improved according to the  Hangzhou Metro Map that has been released  and the proportions and details have been improved. We have a detailed understanding of the rail transit in Hangzhou and Hangzhou metropolitan areas and strictly map them one to one according to the lines that have been opened and operated
